g_1^{-1}((a,\infty]) = \bigcup_1^{\infty}f_j^{-1}((a,\infty])\tag1
x \in g_1^{-1}((a,\infty]) \iff x\in \bigcup_1^{\infty}f_j^{-1}((a,\infty])\tag2
g_1(x)>a \iff \exists j \ f_j(x)>a\tag3
